name: Arboretum Bridge
description:
I was born aboard generational spaceship, Saturn's Spirit, which launched from Earth in the year 2214.  My favorite place on the whole ship is the beautiful and grand arboretum. The glass dome stretches over 5 acres of vegetation. The arboretum provides the ship with food, oxygen and a place for recreation.  

Don't worry the bridge is much sturdier than it appears.
